entry.tran: （构成动词）表示“使处于…状态”，“使成为”，“使进入”;（构成形容词或名词）表示“过程”，“状态”，“状况”
entry.def: En- is added to words to form verbs that describe the process of putting someone into a particular state, condition, or place, or to form adjectives and nouns that describe that process or those states and conditions.
